{"tid":826932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"電話公司CXL/101X 續約條款第一條都唔講","createTime":"2018-09-18T14:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T10:56:03.000Z","uid":105884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1d1d6613addc36656684f820ca72e613ef0919","tid":826932,"uid":105884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"成件事係咁既..電話10月份完約..7月尾打電話叫人續約..<br />\n之後比左個一大堆收費加埋614蚊月費既plan我，就送7500蚊既手機或配件優惠卷..當時我好清楚講明係咪可以買下一部新出既iphone...佢就話有淨機發售可以...今日發現條款寫住 指定小米同蘋果產品唔可以用..今日打去問係咪肯定之後可以用..佢都答我唔到..佢話你份合約係咪完左買唔到？ 嘩..經理都咁唔講道理？等到合約完左買唔到先處理？咁樣份合約都可以生效？<br />\n佢仲一路答多謝我既反映..話同事之前知道我想買新iphone..所以重點銷售，事實係沒提及過條款其實列明是有機會不能買..現在合約已續...有無巴打有好既方法？"},{"pid":"4f7c68b256d3d44d6430fceab97ee99225c4b3cd","tid":826932,"uid":105884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"有無巴打發生同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8f2c06a8fd448bb490f289ed6566099c550d66","tid":826932,"uid":105884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"有同樣情況既黎講下解決方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b75c739627495bcefabdf1d4bb19ca1a575d54","tid":826932,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"唔係淨係小米唔得咩<br />\n<br />\n利申: 聽人講"},{"pid":"3a2675b5f0f4f1f24fb4a9a2d9352b544d71a441","tid":826932,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"佢地都有打嚟話可以拎嚟買iphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我冇答應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7772aaa85a24f136db747b8b266f551e25224e6","tid":826932,"uid":105884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a2675b5f0f4f1f24fb4a9a2d9352b544d71a441","tid":826932,"